{"tid":1255060,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/Xbox One/PC] Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 實現真跨平台聯機","createTime":"2019-06-24T11:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T09:44:06.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47f8d339f6de549aeeae4fc12b0654c3f004bfa9","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2365730600364114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2365730600364114&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=09de4331\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2365730600364114</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/zBxWYxNN/1.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FzBxWYxNN%2F1.jpg%3F&h=74486bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 》是一部&ldquo;現代戰爭&rdquo;系列的重啟作品，也是首部PS4/Xbox One/PC三大平台跨平台聯機的COD遊戲。但是很多玩家認為這種跨平台只是PS4和PC，或者Xbox和PC間的跨平台聯機，而不是真的跨三個平台。為了回應這個謠言遊戲敘事總監推特上展開了問答。<br />\n<br />\n《Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 》的遊戲敘事總監Taylor Kurosaki，在推特上針對遊戲跨平台聯機的真實性和局限性進行了問答，解決了玩家們的煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n要知道，能實現PS4和Xbox One兩大主機平台跨平台聯機的遊戲可不多，《堡壘之夜》和《火箭聯盟》這兩款大作目前做到了。 《Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 》現在也在實現這個目標，但是要知道，PC端的玩家可是可以使用鍵鼠的，這對主機玩家們來說可以算是一種極大的不公平，這次真的要三大平台跨平台聯機了，不知道IW或者動視會採取什麼辦法解決這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 》將於2019年10月25日登陸PS4/Xbox One和PC平台。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/W4J0rG06/2.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FW4J0rG06%2F2.png%3F&h=5e9249ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/mgkYZfDn/3.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FmgkYZfDn%2F3.png%3F&h=c9fb1133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/sgLpv6Gg/4.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FsgLpv6Gg%2F4.png%3F&h=6cadaa63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"784a049d384e12546cb304ff3ee245a3f7843385","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"唔係成日有手掣友話玩慣左手掣會好用過mouse咩? 到時睇下點  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43cd2d3935cfd9d660a322876dabbe8b3f156c8","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942e2acef7184ff8cd063bf5e5fca51859c00c0","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49453cc7254787f4dced5c00e20ff4af58ac88b4","tid":1255060,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"正常係手制同手制連,mouse同mouse連<br />\n有人可能話連server時搵人時用手制搵,玩時即刻改用mouse,就我所知例如fortnite你用手制mode入game的話就算拔左條線佢都唔會認返你個mouse,當你掛機,COD醒目D的話就應該要咁做"},{"pid":"efc568909795561c9f0396909aebcf341f350ebd","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49453cc7254787f4dced5c00e20ff4af58ac88b4","tid":1255060,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"正常係手制同手制連,mouse同mouse連<br />\n有人可能話連server時搵人時用手制搵,玩時即刻改用mouse,就我所知例如fortnite你用手制mode入game的話就算拔左條線佢都唔會認返你個mouse,當你掛機,COD醒目D的話就應該要咁做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"咁樣邊好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068783a04dfa79a0c28ed2a3db15a795b7887ee5","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65df09b9b19755f0a8056e50f9759eaea982e970","tid":1255060,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0